flowchart LR
    App[应用 goroutine] --> Pool[pgxpool]
    Pool --> BE[PostgreSQL Backend]

    BE --> SQLLock[表锁/行锁/咨询锁]
    SQLLock --> HLM[Heavyweight Lock Manager]
    HLM --> LT[LOCKTAG + mode]
    HLM --> G[Granted]
    HLM --> Q[Wait Queue]
    Q --> D[Deadlock Detector]

    BE --> Heap[Heap Tuple Header]
    Heap --> XMAX[xmax/infomask]
    XMAX --> XID[Transaction ID]
    XMAX --> MX[MultiXact]
    XID --> HLM
    MX --> SLRU[MultiXact SLRU]

    BE --> Buf[shared_buffers]
    Buf --> Pin[Buffer Pin]
    Buf --> LW[LWLock]
    LW --> Spin[Spinlock/原子状态]

    Q --> Wait[pg_stat_activity wait_event]
    HLM --> Locks[pg_locks]
    Wait --> Block[pg_blocking_pids]

    BE --> WAL[WAL]
    WAL --> Replica[Physical Replica]
